Hi ChatGPT, I'm drafting a section of my paper on community-led coastal cleanup efforts and would appreciate your help polishing it. Here’s a snippet from my LaTeX document:

\section{Preliminary Observations}
In the past two summers, I have documented multiple volunteer groups along the Pacific coastline engaging in debris removal. These efforts have led to measurable reductions in plastic pollution, improved wildlife habitat, and strengthened local stewardship. However, challenges remain in coordinating resources, securing sustainable funding, and ensuring long-term community engagement. I aim to analyze the factors that contribute to successful outcomes and propose a scalable framework for other regions to adopt.

Here’s a refined version that tightens the language and maintains the first-person perspective:

\section{Preliminary Observations}
Over the past two summers, I have documented numerous volunteer groups along the Pacific coastline proactively conducting debris removal. These coordinated efforts have yielded measurable reductions in plastic pollution, enhanced wildlife habitats, and fostered stronger local stewardship. Despite these successes, coordinating resources, securing sustainable funding, and sustaining long-term community engagement remain significant challenges. In this study, I analyze the critical factors driving successful outcomes and propose a scalable framework that other regions can adapt to achieve similar impacts.
